      <!--//hero-text-block-->
    </div>
    <!--//container-->
  </div>
  <!--//hero-block-->

  <section id="about-section" class="about-section section theme-bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h3 class="section-heading text-center mb-3">About ROCCON</h3>
      <div class="section-intro text-center single-col-max mx-auto mb-4">
        We see a future where land,
        air, sea, space, cognitive, and biotechnological industries are well
        supported to make the Australian digital world safer.
      </div>
      <br />
      <div class="section-intro text-center single-col-max mx-auto mb-4">
        <strong>
          Our vision is simple: to help everyone grow and protect against
          online threats. We're here to make sure that cyber professionals and
          those who need their support can easily connect, creating a strong
          and united community that keeps our digital spaces secure and
          thriving.
        </strong>
      </div>
      <!-- <div class="event-countdown text-center mb-3">
        <h4 class="countdown-intro mb-2 text-center mb-3">
          Event Starts In:
        </h4>
        <div id="countdown-box" class="countdown-box"></div>
      </div> -->
      <!--//event-countdown-->
    {% if tickets_on_sale %}
      <div class="about-cta text-center mb-5">
        <a class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg mb-5" href="{{ ticket_url }}" target="_blank">Get Your Ticket Today</a>
      </div>
    {% endif %}
    </div>
    <!--//container-->

    <div class="media-block theme-bg-primary py-5">
      <div class="container">
        <h4 class="text-white text-center pb-3">The Realms</h4>
        <div class="row text-white text-center">
          <div class="col mb-4 mx-3">
            <div class="realm pb-3"><b>Land</b></div>
            <i style="color: #fff" class="fa-solid fa-truck fa-4x"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="col mb-4 mx-3">
            <div class="realm pb-3"><b>Sea</b></div>
            <i style="color: #fff" class="fa-solid fa-ship fa-4x"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="col mb-4 mx-3">
            <div class="realm pb-3"><b>Air</b></div>
            <i style="color: #fff" class="fa-solid fa-plane-departure fa-4x"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="col mb-4 mx-3">
            <div class="realm pb-3"><b>Space</b></div>
            <i style="color: #fff" class="fa-solid fa-satellite fa-4x"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="col mb-4 mx-3">
            <div class="realm pb-3"><b>Biological</b></div>
            <i style="color: #fff" class="fa-solid fa-dna fa-4x"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="col mb-4 mx-3">
            <div class="realm pb-3"><b>Cognitive</b></div>
            <i style="color: #fff" class="fa-solid fa-brain fa-4x"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!--//container-->
      <div class="container">
        <h4 class="text-white text-center mb-3 mt-5">Previously</h4>
        <div class="section-intro text-center single-col-max mx-auto text-white mb-5">
          ROCCON {{ year - 1 }} brought together some of the brightest minds in physical cybersecurity for a day of inspiring and informative discussions. Held at the iconic Brisbane Powerhouse, the conference explored the future of security across various domains, including land, sea, air, space, biological, and cognitive industries. This year’s theme focused on the convergence of operational technology and cybersecurity, addressing the growing challenges and opportunities in protecting our digital world. The event was a resounding success, with attendees gaining valuable insights and networking with industry leaders.
        </div>
      </div>
      <!--//container-->
    </div>
    <!--//media-block-->
  </section>
  <!--//about-section-->

  <!--speakers-section-->
  <section id="speakers-section" class="speakers-section section active">
    <div class="container">
      <h3 class="section-heading text-center mb-3">Speakers</h3>
      <div class="section-intro text-center single-col-max mx-auto mb-5">
        We have an exciting list of speakers rolling out for our {{ year }} conference,
        check them out:
      </div>
    {% set ns = namespace(speaker_count=0) %}
    {% for speaker in speakers -%}
      {% if ns.speaker_count % 4 == 0 %}
      <div class="row" name="{{ ns.speaker_count }}">
      {% endif %}
      {% set ns.speaker_count = ns.speaker_count + 1 %}
        <div class="col-6 col-lg-3 mb-4">
          <div class="card rounded-0">
            <a href="#{{ speaker['image'] }}" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#{{ speaker['image'] }}"><img src="assets/images/speakers/{{ speaker['image'] }}" class="card-img-top rounded-0" alt=""></a>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title mb-2">{{ speaker['name'] }}</h5>
              <div class="card-text mb-3">
                <div class="meta">{{ speaker['jobtitle'] }}</div>
                <div class="meta">{{ speaker['company'] }}</div>
              </div>
              <a href="#{{ speaker['image'] }}" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#{{ speaker['image'] }}">Read more →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer text-muted">
              <ul class="social-list list-inline mb-0">
                <li class="list-inline-item">
                  <a href="{{ speaker['linkedin'] }}"><i class="fab fa-linkedin-in fa-fw" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% if ns.speaker_count % 4 == 0 %}
        </div>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}

      {% if ns.speaker_count % 4 != 0 %}
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    <!--//container-->
  {% if tickets_on_sale %}
  <div class="speakers-cta text-center py-3">
        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="{{ ticket_url }}" target="_blank">Get Tickets</a>
  </div>
  {% endif %}
  </section>
  <!--//speakers-section-->



  {% if last_year_highlights %}
  <div class="container">
    <hr />
  </div>
  <section id="schedule-section" class="schedule-section section">
    <div class="container">
      <h3 class="section-heading text-center mb-5">{{ year - 1 }} Highlights</h3>
      <div class="desc text-center">
        ROCCON {{ year - 1 }} featured a diverse range of sessions that enthralled the audience. Key highlights included:
      </div>
      <div class="schedule-tab-content tab-content">
        <div class="tab-pane active show" id="tab-1-content" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-1">

          <!-- OPENING KEYNOTE -->
          <div class="item item-talk">
            <div class="meta">
              <h4 class="time mb-3">Nicholas Lindsay</h4>
              <div class="profile">
                <a href="#modal-speaker-4" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#modal-speaker-4"><img
                    class="profile-image rounded-circle mb-2" src="assets/images/speakers/nicholas_lindsay.jpg"
                    alt="" /></a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
              <h3 class="title mb-3">
                Secrets to Success in Dynamic Startups
              </h3>
              <div class="location mb-3">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-satellite me-2"></i>
                <b>Space Realm</b>
              </div>
              <div class="desc">
                Shared his experiences from SpaceX and beyond.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- PRESENTATION 1 -->
          <div class="item item-talk">
            <div class="meta">
              <h4 class="time mb-3">Kylie McDevitt</h4>
              <div class="profile">
                <a href="#modal-speaker-1" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#modal-speaker-1">
                  <img class="profile-image rounded-circle mb-2" src="assets/images/speakers/kylie_mcdevitt.jpg"
                    alt="" /></a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
              <h3 class="title mb-3">
                Enhancing Embedded Security Assessments
              </h3>
              <div class="location mb-3">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-earth-americas me-2"></i>
                <b>Multi Realm</b>
              </div>
              <div class="desc">
                Shared innovative approaches to securing IoT devices, which have become increasingly pervasive in our daily lives.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>


          <!-- PRESENTATION 3 -->
          <div class="item item-talk">
            <div class="meta">
              <h4 class="time mb-3">Bradley Butler</h4>
              <div class="profile">
                <a href="#modal-speaker-6" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#modal-speaker-6">
                  <img class="profile-image rounded-circle mb-2" src="assets/images/speakers/bradley_butler.jpg"
                    alt="" /></a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
              <h3 class="title mb-3">
                Securing the Seas: From Pirate Threats to Cyber Attacks
              </h3>
              <div class="location mb-3">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-ship me-2"></i>
                <b>Sea Realm</b>
              </div>
              <div class="desc">
                Took attendees on a journey through the evolution of maritime security and the strategies used to combat modern threats.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

 


          <!-- PRESENTATION 13 -->
          <div class="item item-talk">
            <div class="meta">
              <h4 class="time mb-3">Sanja Marais</h4>
              <div class="profile">
                <a href="#modal-speaker-5" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#modal-speaker-5"><img
                    class="profile-image rounded-circle mb-2" src="assets/images/speakers/sanja_marais.jpg"
                    alt="" /></a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
              <h3 class="title mb-3">
                Guardians of the Health Tech Galaxy: Cybersecurity Edition
              </h3>
              <div class="location mb-3">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-dna me-2"></i>
                <b>Biological Realm</b>
              </div>
              <div class="desc">
                Captivated attendees with exploring the future of cybersecurity in healthcare.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- NETWORKING SESSION -->
          <div class="item item-other">
            <div class="meta">
              <h4 class="time mb-3">Closing Reception</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
              <h3 class="title mb-3">
                Networking Session
              </h3>
              <div class="desc">
                Provided a relaxed environment for attendees to connect and discuss the day’s events. Where better than by the beautiful Brisbane River?
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="desc text-center">
        These sessions, along with many others, provided actionable takeaways that attendees can apply within their organisations.
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <!--//schedule-section-->
  {% endif %}

  {% if tickets_on_sale %}
  <section id="tickets-section" class="tickets-section section theme-bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h3 class="section-heading text-center mb-3">Tickets</h3>

      <div class="row pricing mb-2 justify-content-center">

        <!--//col-->
        <div class="col-12 col-md-4 p-2 p-lg-4">
          <div class="card card-special rounded-0 border-0">
            <div class="card-body p-0">
              <div class="heading text-center p-3">
                <h4 class="text-white mb-0">Early Bird</h4>
